ns0:DescribedValueSet.ns0:Purpose: (Clinical Focus: This value set contains concepts that represent repair of the uterus performed by any approach.),(Data Element Scope: This value set may use the Quality Data Model (QDM) category related to Procedure. The intent of this value set is to identify patients who have had a metroplasty, uteroplasty, hysteroplasty, or repair of the uterus procedure.),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes only relevant concepts associated with SNOMED CT codes that represent metroplasty, uteroplasty, hysteroplasty, and repair of the uterus procedures.),(Exclusion Criteria: No exclusions.)
